First American Financial Corp., the
second-largest U.S. title insurer, promoted Mark Seaton to chief
financial officer.  Seaton, who was senior vice president of finance, replaces
CFO Max Valdes, who is retiring after 25 years with the company,
 Santa Ana , California-based First American said today in a
statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
